    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an exceptional 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in concours-level condition. This specimen features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, boasting individual throttle bodies and a factory 8,000 RPM redline. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission delivers crisp, tactile engagement, paired with a variable M-differential for precise power delivery. This vehicle has undergone rigorous preventative maintenance, including rod bearing replacement and rear subframe reinforcement. The chassis retains its factory rigidity, and the suspension remains taut with no bushing deflection. Finished in a depth-rich Carbon Black over Cinnamon Nappa leather, the aesthetics match the mechanical perfection. No VANOS rattle, no pixel degradation, and a completely dry undercarriage make this a definitive collector-grade example.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
