      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, collector-grade vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. This car has been meticulously garage-kept and maintained with an open-checkbook policy. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero rock chips or swirl marks, protected by a professional ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary\u2014the premium leather remains supple and scent-free, with no visible wear on the bolsters or touchpoints. Mechanically, it is flawless, featuring a fully documented service history and incredibly low original miles. Every switch, button, and electronic feature functions perfectly. This is a rare opportunity to own a turnkey masterpiece that satisfies even the most discerning enthusiast. No accidents, no stories, just pure automotive perfection.",
